**Brap Music Promo (2010)
Features:
Cris.mic, Stoney, Kapulot & OG

Production from: 
Cris.mic, Stoney, Kapulot, Motley & Mantik

2010
After the underground favorite Mancsta Music Vol 2 168 edtion in 2009 which was recieved well by a hardcore set of fans that copped a copy or downloaded for FREE, MancStar started to focus on the next moves.
Always staying creative with rehersals, recording and producing Cris.mic stepped up for his first release as a solo artist. 
After gainin his stripes on the Manchester scene since 2004 supporting acts such as Dilated Peoples and Big Brovaz Cris.mic brought his first solo effort the 'Brap Music Promo' with plans to bring the Brap Music Mixtape in the near future.
data.text: The first CD was released in 2005 and since then MancStar has released 6 projects to date. D'Arcangels/MancStar have supported acts such as Skinnyman, Klashnekoff, Broke N English, Children Of The Damned, Dilated Peoples & Big Brovaz
